Finel-Honigman Says G20 Will Recapitalize Banks (Audio)

-- B y  
-- 
2011-10-18T15:29:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-18/finel-honigman-says-g20-will-recapitalize-banks-audio-.html
Irene Finel-Honigman, adjunct 
professor of international and public affairs at Columbia 
University, says G20 bank recapitalization is more crucial than 
the restructuring of Greek debt.  Finel-Honigman talks with  
Kathleen Hays on "The Hays Advantage" on Bloomberg Radio.  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 23:12
 